headline: Goldman Sachs Raises Stanley Black & Decker (SWK) PT to $84 After Margin-Driven Q4 Beat
summary: Stanley Black & Decker, Inc. (NYSE:SWK) is included among the 13 Cheapest Dividend Aristocrats to Invest in. On February 6, Goldman Sachs analyst Joe Ritchie raised his price recommendation on Stanley Black & Decker, Inc. (NYSE:SWK) to $84 from $78. The analyst reiterated a Neutral rating on the stock.
